{
  "stem": "1473.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And my aunt said, we'll buy you a hot chocolate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "There was this big cafe on the corner, where the trolley car stopped at the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It was a few steps up, three steps up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And there was a big sign saying, 'Dogs and Jews, entrance forbidden.' And I remember my mother saying, look at this, and just remember this.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "So we took the trolley back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We were frozen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And then there were, I guess, letters and telegrams, back and forth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father went to Belgium.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was successful in-- you see, you got to the German frontier, and to the border guards.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you told the border guards, we are leaving for-- we're going to Belgium.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They searched you, to make sure you had no more than 10 marks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were, I remember, courteous.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's it!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Those were the Germans!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, though, you had to have a-- a guide to bring your way into Belgium.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because the Belgian would reject you at the border.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They rejected the Jews at the border.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was very bad, if you were rejected, to get back into their hands, then.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I understand you-- you were then put into-- in those days, they didn't have the death camps yet, but the concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father and his brother-in-law and a relative of his brother-in-law got to Antwerp successfully, where my father had relatives who were nice people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very nice people, who had gone-- whose parents had gone from Poland to Antwerp, and who had done well.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So then they sent my mother and her sister all the necessary guidelines to-- to join them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we left by train, later that December, to Aachen, in Germany, which was the Belgian border.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
